This paper involves the use of spiking neural networks as classifiers and a genetic algorithm to evolve neural structures, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses reinforcement learning, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The robotic navigation task mentioned in the abstract suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of robotics (cs.RO) or systems and control (cs.SY).
